    <title>github+hexo+next搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="https://dongming.com/2019/06/28/github-hexo-next%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>https://dongming.com/2019/06/28/github-hexo-next搭建个人博客/</id>
    <published>2019-06-28T03:40:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-06-28T04:07:32.406Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用github与hexo搭建个人blog，使用next主题<br>配置页面效果:<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/9f0e90cc32c2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考文章</a></p><hr><h2 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a><strong>常用命令</strong></h2><ul><li>创建新文章<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n &apos;article title&apos;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><ul><li>重新生成并部署<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><ul><li>本地预览<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://localhost:4000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><ul><li>提交<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h2 id="MarkDown语法-参考文章"><a href="#MarkDown语法-参考文章" class="headerlink" title="MarkDown语法:参考文章"></a>MarkDown语法:<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/191d1e21f7ed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考文章</a></h2><p>文章中添加图片</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.安装插件:npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line">2.hexo的_config.yml中的post_asset_folder修改为true</span><br><span class="line">3.hexo n &apos;new_blog&apos;创建新文章后，会生成new_blog与new_blog.md</span><br><span class="line">4.将需要在new_blog.md中添加的图片放在new_blog目录内</span><br><span class="line">5.在new_blog.md中使用markdown语法添加图片，例如: ![](/new_blog/test.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
    
